The draft sentence, drafted by Minister Olga S<0xC3><0xA1>nchez Cordero, proposed the declaration of the decree as unconstitutional, because the regulation of radio and television is an attribution reserved by law to the Federal Telecommunications Commission (Cofetel), in contravention of the principles of hierarchical subordination and reservation of law.
Only Zald<0xC3><0xAD>var, Jorge Mario Pardo, Margarita Luna and even S<0xC3><0xA1>nchez Cordero voted in favour of the project.
